      "module_path": "hook",
      "docs": "Guard hook handler for block-direct-git-ops. Modified in this track in two ways: (1) T001/IN-03 stage (a): handle scans the raw HookInput.command string for SOTP_GUARDED_GIT (exact match) before calling check_commands, and returns block early if the token is found — SimpleCommand does not carry the raw string, so this scan must happen at the usecase layer; (2) T006/CN-06: gains a hooks_path_configured: bool private field injected by HookDispatchInteractor, used to implement runtime fail-closed behavior — when hooks_path_configured is false and a git command is detected, handle returns block before checking normal policy. Private fields: hooks_path_configured: bool.",
